The paper deals with the analysis of a MIMO-CDMA channel, which is a topic related to information theory and communication systems (cs.IT and cs.COMM). The use of the replica method to evaluate the spectral efficiency is a common technique in statistical physics and machine learning, which are also relevant fields for this paper (cs.MA and cs.SI).
